---
---
<section id="about" style="background:#071A35;padding:7rem 2.5rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;right:0;width:50%;height:100%;z-index:0;opacity:0.1;">
    <img src="/global-network.png" alt="" aria-hidden="true" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:left center;" />
  </div>

  <div style="max-width:1440px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:5rem;align-items:center;position:relative;z-index:1;">

    <div style="position:relative;border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;">
      <img src="/about-leaders.png" alt="Global health leaders facing a connected world" style="width:100%;height:480px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:14px;display:block;" />
      <div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,transparent 40%,rgba(4,19,38,0.85) 100%);border-radius:14px;"></div>
      <div style="position:absolute;bottom:1.5rem;left:1.5rem;right:1.5rem;">
        <div style="background:rgba(4,19,38,0.75);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);border:1px solid rgba(214,164,58,0.2);border-radius:10px;padding:1rem 1.25rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;">
          <i class="ti ti-globe" style="font-size:28px;color:#D6A43A;flex-shrink:0;"></i>
          <div>
            <div style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:800;color:#fff;line-height:1;">70+ Countries</div>
            <div style="font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);margin-top:2px;">Represented in our global cohort</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p style="font-size:11px;letter-spacing:3px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#1CC7C9;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:1rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;">
        <span style="width:20px;height:1px;background:#1CC7C9;display:inline-block;"></span>
        What Is GHO Academy
      </p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(38px,4vw,58px);font-weight:800;color:#F8F8F8;text-transform:uppercase;line-height:0.95;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        The Leadership Education<br /><span style="color:#D6A43A;">Global Health Was Missing</span>
      </h2>
      <p style="font-size:15px;color:rgba(248,248,248,0.65);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
        The global health system produces brilliant technical experts. It rarely produces bold, strategic leaders capable of navigating power, mobilizing funding, influencing policy, and driving systemic change.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size:15px;color:rgba(248,248,248,0.65);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        GHO Academy fills that gap. In 8 weeks, you gain the tools, frameworks, network, and mindset that 17 years of global health leadership taught Dr. Bain — compressed into the most practical executive course in the field.
      </p>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0.625rem;margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
        {["Oxford-Affiliated Faculty","African-Led","AI-Integrated","Cohort-Based Live Learning","Stakeholder Capstone"].map(tag => (
          <span style="font-size:12px;background:rgba(214,164,58,0.1);color:#D6A43A;border:1px solid rgba(214,164,58,0.25);padding:5px 12px;border-radius:20px;font-weight:600;">{tag}</span>
        ))}
      </div>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1rem;">
        {[
          { num: "30–50",  label: "Cohort size",         sub: "Intentionally small for impact"     },
          { num: "10",     label: "Live modules",         sub: "Each 2 hours with Dr. Bain"         },
          { num: "Global", label: "Participant network",  sub: "Africa, UK, North America & beyond" },
          { num: "Real",   label: "Capstone outcomes",    sub: "Pitched to policymakers & funders"  },
        ].map(c => (
          <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(214,164,58,0.15);padding:1.25rem;border-radius:10px;border-top:3px solid #D6A43A;transition:background 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.background='rgba(214,164,58,0.07)'" onmouseout="this.style.background='rgba(255,255,255,0.04)'">
            <div style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-size:32px;font-weight:800;color:#D6A43A;line-height:1;margin-bottom:4px;">{c.num}</div>
            <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#fff;margin-bottom:2px;">{c.label}</div>
            <div style="font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);">{c.sub}</div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    #about > div:last-child { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; gap: 3rem !important; }
    #about > div:last-child > div:first-child img { height: 320px !important; }
    #about > div:last-child > div:last-child > div:last-child { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr !important; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    #about { padding: 5rem 1.5rem !important; }
    #about > div:last-child > div:last-child > div:last-child { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
  }
</style>
